HETEOS - Hypermdia As The Engine Of Application State

Heteos is the way to guide the interactions of the client with Restful Services 
by providing hypermedia links with the response and indicate available action and resources 

Benefits 
Discoverability - Client can discover available action and resources dynamically by following links which coming in response 
Decoupling : client are less dependent on fixed URL's 
Guidance : clients are guided on how to interact with the API 
